data.description: Mansions of San Tan! Major price reduction! Paid off solar, Pool, views, All New A/C's and massive lot! This beautiful two story energy efficient, Paid solar nestled on a cul-de-sac lot is the one! Double doors open to the welcoming interior featuring a lovely foyer, trending palette, archways and tasteful flooring tile and soft carpeting throughout. The perfectly sized living room is an ideal space for receiving guests. Continue to the huge family room with media niches, perfect for entertaining gatherings. The formal dining room is poised to host dinner parties. Cooking is a delight in this gorgeous kitchen, boasting a plethora of wood cabinetry, brand new stainless appliances, tile backsplash, granite counters, island and pantry. Don't miss the spacious loft as a theater or game room! The main bedroom downstairs w/a private bathroom & a walk-in closet is designed for privacy & convenience. Additionally, there's a BIG primary suite showcasing vaulted ceilings & an immaculate ensuite w/dual vanities, a separate shower, & a walk-in closet. You'll love the expansive backyard for summer cookouts & al fresco dining. Offering a relaxing covered patio, a BBQ grill, a fire pit, a pergola, a sparkling blue pool, a play area, & multiple seating areas. This gem won't disappoint you! Visit right now!
